]},"primaryContentSections":[{"kind":"declarations","declarations":[{"platforms":["macOS"],"languages":["swift"],"tokens":[{"text":"@","kind":"attribute"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:ScM","text":"MainActor","kind":"attribute"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"struct","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"ConstrainedFill","kind":"identifier"},{"text":"<","kind":"text"},{"text":"Content","kind":"genericParameter"},{"text":"> ","kind":"text"},{"text":"where","kind":"keyword"},{"text":" ","kind":"text"},{"text":"Content","kind":"typeIdentifier"},{"text":" : ","kind":"text"},{"preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI4ViewP","text":"View","kind":"typeIdentifier"}]}]},{"kind":"content","content":[{"anchor":"overview","text":"Overview","level":2,"type":"heading"},{"content":[{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This view was initially provided to allow a layout arrangement that can be achieved","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"using ","type":"text"},{"code":".minFrameSize","type":"codeVoice"},{"text":". It is left here in case further uses are found. This view may be","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"deleted in the future.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}],"name":"Note","type":"aside","style":"note"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Content larger that the available space will overflow outside of the view while still respecting","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the given alignment. Each view in the content is constrained individually, even if one view","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"overflows over the available space, all other views will resize themselves to the available","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"space.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Views in content are placed in an implicit ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"ZStack"},{"text":". Providing more that one view will stack","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"them on top of each other, the last view provided appears at the front of the stack.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"Internally, each view in content is individually constrained to a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":"frame"},{"text":" sized to the available","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"space.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"This view provides a behaviour that ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".frame"},{"text":" is unable to support: using a ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".frame"},{"text":" that expands","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to occupy all available space (with ","type":"text"},{"type":"codeVoice","code":".infinity"},{"text":" for width and height) will behave the same while","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"the content is smaller that the available space. However, if the content is larger, then the","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"size of the frame will expand to the size of the content. This view ","type":"text"},{"inlineContent":[{"text":"always","type":"text"}],"type":"strong"},{"text":" contrains the content","type":"text"},{"text":" ","type":"text"},{"text":"to the available space.","type":"text"}],"type":"paragraph"}]}],"references":{"doc://PreviewUtilities/documentation/PreviewUtilities/ConstrainedFill/init(alignment:content:)":{"type":"topic","fragments":[{"kind":"identifier","text":"init"},{"kind":"text","text":"("},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"alignment"},{"kind":"text","text":": "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Alignment","preciseIdentifier":"s:7SwiftUI9AlignmentV"},{"kind":"text","text":", "},{"kind":"externalParam","text":"content"},{"kind":"text","text":": () -> "},{"kind":"typeIdentifier","text":"Content"},{"kind":"text","text":")"}],"kind":"symbol","identifier":"doc:\/\/PreviewUtilities\/documentation\/PreviewUtilities\/ConstrainedFill\/init(alignment:content:)","title":"init(